        Draws a single-object on top of a RGB-stack
        Parameters:
        object - the object to draw
        stack - the RGB-stack to draw upon
        attributes - attributes for each object when drawing
        iteration - the current iteration
        restrictTo - a restriction on which part of stack we draw onto to (considered in terms of the possibly-zoomed pixel cooridinates)
        Throws:
        OperationFailedException
